# <%= appName %> — Microservice Architecture

Independently deployable services with explicit contracts.

## Layout

```
services/
  api-gateway/     # edge routing
  <service-name>/  # one folder per service
shared/
  contracts/       # DTOs, event schemas
  kernel/          # shared types
  infrastructure/  # service mesh, tracing config
```

## Communication

- Synchronous: HTTP/gRPC via API gateway
- Asynchronous: message bus (`my add queue` / Phase 4 event system)

Services **must not** import each other's internal code — only `shared/contracts`.

## Local development

```bash
docker compose -f docker-compose.services.yml up
```
